wiki.summary: “THANK GOD” is the second track on UTOPIA, and a collaboration with another Kanye West protege, KayCyy. Travis Scott delves into the complexities of life and expresses his gratitude for every moment he gets to live it. The song starts by Travis embracing the chaos of life while celebrating self-discovery and personal growth. With a mix of darkness and brightness, the song highlights the importance of living life to the fullest and finding gratitude in every moment. Read more on Last.fm.
